Screen Open 0,640,256,4,$8000
Curs Off : Flash Off : Cls 0
Double Buffer : Autoback 0
'
Wb 3d Eye 0,0,450
Wb 3d Centre 320,128
'
While Mouse Key=0
   Add CX,1,0 To 359
   Add CY,2,0 To 359
   Add CZ,3,0 To 359
   Wb 3d Angle CX,CY,CZ
   '
   Wb 3d Point -100,100,-100 : X0=Wb 3d X : Y0=Wb 3d Y : Z0=Wb 3d Z
   Wb 3d Point 100,100,-100 : X1=Wb 3d X : Y1=Wb 3d Y : Z1=Wb 3d Z
   Wb 3d Point 100,-100,-100 : X2=Wb 3d X : Y2=Wb 3d Y : Z2=Wb 3d Z
   Wb 3d Point -100,-100,-100 : X3=Wb 3d X : Y3=Wb 3d Y : Z3=Wb 3d Z
   ZA=(Z0+Z1+Z2+Z3)/4
   '
   Wb 3d Point -100,100,100 : X4=Wb 3d X : Y4=Wb 3d Y : Z4=Wb 3d Z
   Wb 3d Point 100,100,100 : X5=Wb 3d X : Y5=Wb 3d Y : Z5=Wb 3d Z
   Wb 3d Point 100,-100,100 : X6=Wb 3d X : Y6=Wb 3d Y : Z6=Wb 3d Z
   Wb 3d Point -100,-100,100 : X7=Wb 3d X : Y7=Wb 3d Y : Z7=Wb 3d Z
   ZB=(Z4+Z5+Z6+Z7)/4
   '
   If ZA>ZB
      Ink 1 : Polygon X0,Y0 To X1,Y1 To X2,Y2 To X3,Y3
      Ink 2 : Polygon X4,Y4 To X5,Y5 To X6,Y6 To X7,Y7
   Else 
      Ink 2 : Polygon X4,Y4 To X5,Y5 To X6,Y6 To X7,Y7
      Ink 1 : Polygon X0,Y0 To X1,Y1 To X2,Y2 To X3,Y3
   End If 
   Screen Swap 
   Cls 0
Wend 
